Stand up. Come on. Stand up.

00:04:25.398 --> 00:04:28.567
Good job.

00:04:28.567 --> 00:04:31.370
You mind if I use your lawyers
for various things?

00:04:31.370 --> 00:04:33.773
I could use
some good lawyers too.

00:04:33.773 --> 00:04:37.243
-Only Trump would compliment
nuns on their record in court.

00:04:37.243 --> 00:04:38.678
[ Laughter ]

00:04:38.678 --> 00:04:41.547
"God would have been very proud
of how litigious you are."

00:04:41.547 --> 00:04:43.415
Such a weird sequencing, too.

00:04:43.415 --> 00:04:44.750
Like, "Give it up for the nuns,

00:04:44.750 --> 00:04:48.654
but also, the real heroes,
their legal team."

00:04:48.654 --> 00:04:50.956
And the woman you see behind
Trump during that speech

00:04:50.956 --> 00:04:54.193
is his spiritual advisor,
friend, and pastor, Paula White.

00:04:54.193 --> 00:04:55.995
